title: Who's Got Next with Nike's Jasmine Watkins
itunes:title: Who's Got Next with Nike's Jasmine Watkins
description:
Miles and Jack were pleased to be joined by Nike's Sr. Manager Community and incredible NBA Twitter follow Jasmine Watkins for the latest episode of Mad Boosties! The trio discussed Minnesota's ALL-IN push and whether we should expect the Timberwolves to take a significant step next year and plenty more.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
